                    <h1 class="mb-1">Use Rain Harvesting or Grey Water</h1>
                    <p>Water collected from these techniques can be used to water your garden.</p>
                
                </div>
                

                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">

                    <img src="images/watertank.jpg" alt="" class="tips-image">

                </div>


                </div>

